
1. Get the source: 

    wget https://github.com/mcvaneede/RMINC/raw/master/releases/RMINC_0.5.tar.gz

2. Add the missing NAMESPACE file to the source (needed for R 3.x): 

    tar xzf RMINC_0.5.tar.gz
    cp NAMESPACE RMINC/
    tar czf RMINC_0.5_namespace.tar.gz RMINC

2. Load the minc-toolkit and R modules this version will depend on, e.g. 

    module load minc-toolkit/1.0.01
    module load R/3.1.1

3. Configure and build

    R CMD INSTALL RMINC_0.5_namespace.tar.gz \
        --library=/opt/quarantine/RMINC/0.5:minc-toolkit-1.0.01:R-3.1.1/build \
        --configure-args='--with-build-path=/opt/quarantine/minc-toolkit/1.0.01/build'
